    synPUF

    Source: R/mod_demo_sqlite.R
    synPUF.Rd

    Overview

    This dataset contains a 10 person subset of the CMS 2008-2010 Data Entrepreneurs’ Synthetic Public Use File (DE-SynPUF) from OHDSI.

    Details

    • Information on the SynPUF data source is available here

    • CDM 5.2.2 DDL for the OHDSI supported DBMSs is available here

    • Notes Obtained from MTSamples.com

    Usage

    synPUF

    Format

    A data frame with 23 rows and 2 variables:

    table_name

    character: The table name in OMOP v5.2.2

    table_data

    list: The table data, in OMOP v5.2.2

    ...
